Package com.rosivanyshyn.controller.other.order

package com.rosivanyshyn.controller.other.order
This is order controllers package. CreateOrderController - to add new order to database and redirect to apartments JSP. DeleteOrderController - to delete order from database (if order created by current user) and redirect to apartments JSP. GetAllOrdersController - to get all users orders (paginated)(for moderator request) and forward to all orders JSP. GetCreateOrderFormController - to get JSP form for create new order. GetFewOrdersController - to get current user orders (paginated) and forward to orders JSP.
